
'''= Article: Market-Protocol Fit. By Sam Hart, Laura Lotti, Toby Shorin. The Other Internet, 2020'''

URL = https://otherinter.net/Market-Protocol-Fit_OtherInternet_2020-04.pdf


=Description=

"Decentralized protocols must rely on headless branding and cooperative incentive structures to evolve. We call this market-protocol fit and describe the phases of this challenging process. While product-market fit is concerned with building an agile team to find and fill market demand, market-protocol fit begins with a broad distribution of tokens, followed by permissionless narrative formation and product innovation which activates them in useful ways."

(https://otherinter.net/research/market-protocol-fit/)


